Hi, I'm trying to set up an engine cylinder simulation, and would like
to incorporate inlet and exhaust valves. Is it possible to set the valve
coefficient to be a function of time?
In Python, it seems that it can be set to a function of delta_p - would 
it be possible in Matlab, either with the Reactor class, or perhaps 
modifying the reactor_ode file?

Thanks,
Michael
